gajendra is a 2004 tamil language action film directed by suresh krishna .   the film features vijayakanth , flora and laya in lead roles .   the film , produced by v. a. durai , had musical score by deva and was released on 26 august 2004 to negative reviews .   the film is remake of telugu blockbuster film simhadri and was later dubbed in hindi as return of khuda gawah .